{"word":"H2403 - חַטָּאָה - chaṭṭâʼâh - khat-taw-aw' - Punishment","slug":"H2403","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חַטָּאָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>chaṭṭâʼâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khat-taw-aw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Punishment"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05D8;&#x05BC;&#x05D0;&#x05EA;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D7;&#x05D8;&#x05BC;&#x05D0;&#x05D4; - chat&#x0323;t&#x0323;a&#x0302;'a&#x0302;h  chat&#x0323;t&#x0323;a&#x0302;'th</b> - <i>khat-taw-aw', khat-tawth'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H2398\">H2398</a>; an <i>offence</i> (sometimes habitual <i>sinfulness</i>), and its penalty, occasion, sacrifice, or expiation; also (concretely) an <i>offender: - </i>punishment (of sin), purifying (-fication for sin), sin (-ner, offering)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2398\">H2398</a>, <a href=\"#/H2399\">H2399</a>, <a href=\"#/H2400\">H2400</a>, <a href=\"#/H2401\">H2401</a>"}]}